cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.LO, cs.SY 

The paper deals with stochastic games, which are a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves algorithms for computing Pareto curves, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.DS). The paper also uses techniques from logic (cs.LO) and control theory (cs.SY) to prove decidability results.
